      "content": "My frontend stack in 2026 ⚡\n\n⚛️ React 18 — component-driven UI with hooks\n📘 TypeScript — strong typing, fewer bugs, better DX\n🗂️ Redux Toolkit — predictable and scalable state management\n\nEach tool solves a specific problem. Together they make a solid, maintainable architecture for any project.",
